snow comb
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a machine shearing comb that leaves a certain length of wool for protection on sheep grazed in high country areas.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
