Citations
Date: 17/7/1954
Source: Press, The
Author:
Vol / Page: 5
Edition:
Quote: Snow comb - a special type of comb used in shearing machines which leaves more wool on the sheep than an ordinary comb, meant for use in the high country where sheep are exposed to the cold.
